<div class="cont-main">
  <h1>About Us</h1>
  <div class="cont">
    <p>
        Funfooding.com is online and mobile food sharing website that connects diners with local people and aspiring chefs serving home cooked food.
  The idea is to provide diners with unlimited varied options available in and around their vicinity. In other words, in your neck of the woods.<br />
 
        A diner can place an order a takeout for an immediate or scheduled for later with the option to pick up or get delivered.
        <br /><br />
        Want home cooked food but no time to cook? <br />
        Search for people in your area who is sharing their meal.<br />
        <br />
        Want home cooked but not in the mood to cook <br />
        Search for people in your area who is sharing their meal at that hour.
          <br /><br />
        <b>We aspire to make your fooding experience fun!</b>
        Have new ideas? @Html.ActionLink("Talk", "Contact", "Company") to us. We are all ears!
         
  </div>

</div>
